4
00:00:04,540 --> 00:00:05,690
the Oslo Freedom Forum,

5
00:00:05,690 --> 00:00:09,210
one of the largest human rights conferences
in the world.

6
00:00:09,210 --> 00:00:10,360
We met up with Mu Sochua,

7
00:00:10,360 --> 00:00:12,620
a former member of the Cambodian Parliament,

8
00:00:12,620 --> 00:00:14,459
now turned rights activist.

9
00:00:14,459 --> 00:00:16,049
She sat down with Shelley Zhang to discuss

10
00:00:16,049 --> 00:00:18,970
